{"id":"c162f3df-b0b6-40a3-a6d1-8f0a027e162b","name":"Foreclosure Taskforce","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>                                                      The Foreclosure Taskforce from Blue Archive</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The Foreclosure Taskforce is the final remaining club within Abydos High. Abydos was a formerly thriving and school but due to desertification most of the cities' buildings have been covered in sand and ruined. Abydos is also in huge debt, with mercenaries constantly attacking in an attempt to claim the school</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_2fdc18a7-62ff-447a-bf9b-1c4c46f24aa5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_31ae6105-1927-42f2-8ec5-6dcea8d25b65.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_a7888a32-8c8b-4777-ae08-1fc57d56706d.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_2148787f-f404-404f-a3c1-6eae1cf78b3b.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_ab6c7251-39de-4724-b70d-734e4f8d5b40.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bad4325c-08c2-4346-80e6-a34035311038_character-hoshino-takanashi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 203, 247)\"><strong><em>Hoshino Takanashi</em></strong></span></a></p><p>Hoshino is the Chairwomen of the Foreclosure Taskforce. Hoshino speaks like an aunt, usually playing around and napping instead of doing her work, leading to her getting scolded by everyone but on the battlefield, she is a force to be reckoned with</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_270f3a0a-4a58-4def-96f5-6a959a99d9b8.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_497231a1-214c-428a-bac8-ff92845053f6.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 61, 149)\"><strong>Serika Kuromi</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Serika is the Secretary of the Foreclosure Taskforce. Serika has difficulty expressing her true emotions, appearing short-tempered and easily embarrassed, but in reality is kind and gentle</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_f4ecd059-2b20-4265-a044-20805def6da8.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_25bc5126-4245-4386-afab-51cce0125489.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ae26e4e3-df9b-4480-b519-cbbbe343a692_character-shiroko-sunaookami\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 212, 255)\"><strong><em>Shiroko Sunaookami</em></strong></span></a></p><p>Shiroko is the Field Captain of the Foreclosure Taskforce. Shiroko is an athletic and quiet person, showing little emotion and few words but deeply cares about Abydos and her friends, willing to do anything to revitalize the school</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_19b04602-04af-4bcb-a2bb-9ee92b4cb310.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"placeholder-nsfw.webp","creator":"FifthBorn","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","📺 Anime","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":12164,"messages":404226,"created_at":"2023-12-24T08:50:34.631367+00:00"}